track_title: Old Baldy Trail from Madera Canyon to Summit

track_notes: This is a loop hike to do 2 10-pointers in a single day.  Its a full day with short time on the peaks.  Josephine is a very tough bushwhack for the half-mile or so from Super Trail to the summit, but otherwise this hike is on well-established trails.
track_title: Loop for Josephine Peak and Mt Wrightson
